GABRIEL SANCHEZ-MARTINEZ: Yeah.

00:17:39.820 --> 00:17:43.019
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE] the
bus exactly where it is.

00:17:43.019 --> 00:17:44.310
GABRIEL SANCHEZ-MARTINEZ: Yeah.

