00:23:20.630 --> 00:23:22.350
I'm not sure.

00:23:22.350 --> 00:23:22.850
So--

00:23:22.850 --> 00:23:24.340
AUDIENCE: That's quite
a medical problem.

00:23:24.340 --> 00:23:25.970
GABRIEL SANCHEZ-MARTINEZ:
So, yeah.

00:23:25.970 --> 00:23:28.550
So a train rear-ended
another one.

00:23:28.550 --> 00:23:30.680
It wasn't too bad.

