I don't think
anybody was killed.

00:23:33.230 --> 00:23:36.350
But, yeah, so there
are advisory signals

00:23:36.350 --> 00:23:40.160
along the track that say, you
should go or you should not go.

00:23:40.160 --> 00:23:42.320
Or you should go slowly.

00:23:42.320 --> 00:23:45.271
But it's up to the driver
to regulate that speed.

00:23:45.271 --> 00:23:47.646
AUDIENCE: On the Green Line
as well one of the provisions

00:23:47.646 --> 00:23:49.363
is on the wayside,
the signal [INAUDIBLE]

